variation in opinion across the demographic spectrum in the south 
where thrifts have fared worst 49 percent rated them safe in the 
northeast 56 percent called them safe that gap slightly exceeded 
the margin of error plus or minus 3 percentage points 
the poll was conducted by the ap and media general inc a 
