35 rem roetgen equivalent man for exposure to radiation that 
figure has a comfortable margin of safety built into it izrael said 
izrael said the area of the three republics where the current 
level of radiation from both the environment and existing food 
supplies would expose residents to more than 35 rem includes 4000 
square miles including about 640 settlements with 230000 people 
that includes 800 square miles in the russian republic 600 
