scrutinize suspiciouslooking passengers 
it also complained that in some instances warnings of terrorist 
plans were not relayed to all pan am security workers in one 
incident all pan am security employees at frankfurt and paris were 
not told of a warning received about two middle eastern women who 
were planning to place explosives aboard a plane the report did not 
