grassroots movements to rid residential areas of gang headquarters 
and offices 
the strongest of those movements evicted a yamaguchigumi 
affiliate from a residential area in hamamatsu central japan and 
the gang today is on the verge of disbanding 
headquarters of both the yamaguchigumi and the ichiwakai are in 
expensive residential districts in kobe but their presence has not 
faced serious local opposition 
