heidi holland has made the journey from 
offbroadway to broadway with her wit and wisdom intact in fact 
she has gotten better although shed be the first to deny it 
heidi is the insecure heroine of the heidi chronicles wendy 
wassersteins funny feminist travelogue that takes theatergoers from 
the late 1960s to the present the play now on view at broadways 
plymouth theater after a successful run at playwrights horizons 
remains one of the unqualified joys of the new york theater season 
in a series of sketches wasserstein traces heidis changing 
ideas about herself about men and about other women heidi an art 
