broadway but he hasnt diluted its effectiveness large slide 
projections that pinpoint specific historical moments from vietnam 
war protests to the first rumbles of womens as well as gay 
liberation enhance its appeal snippets of old pop music also help 
anchor the play in the particular time periods 
at the center of the play stands joan allens radiant performance 
as heidi she projects an intelligence and likability that never 
waver during the characters many moments of selfdoubt its a 
richly drawn portrait 
